---
// PurposeJourney.astro
import Button from './Button.astro';
---
<section class="purpose-journey-panel" id="purpose">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid-24">
      
      <!-- Left Split: The Purpose Quote -->
      <div class="split-left">
        <div class="header-text">
          <span class="label">Our Purpose</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="quote">
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>To ignite meaningful</span></span>
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>and lasting transformations</span></span>
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>in the workplace.</span></span>
        </h2>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Split: The Journey & Core Identity -->
      <div class="split-right">
        <h3 class="heading">
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>When you lean in and</span></span>
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>step into the</span></span>
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>transformation journey,</span></span>
          <span class="reveal-text"><span>deeply-rooted change happens.</span></span>
        </h3>
        
        <div class="journey-content">
          <p class="paragraph">
            <strong>AT THE CENTER</strong> of who we are as an organization is <strong>JESUS CHRIST</strong>, who holds the power for genuine transformation. Our values, principles and strategies are rooted in biblical truth.
          </p>
          <p class="paragraph">
            <strong>AT VANGUARD</strong>, we believe that we are His vessels. We have a responsibility to pour out into the lives of others because God has already poured out into our own hearts.
          </p>
          <blockquote class="scripture">
            “For we are His workmanship, created in Christ Jesus for good works, which God prepared beforehand that we should walk in them.”
            <br>
            <span class="reference">- Ephesians 2:10</span>
          </blockquote>
          
          <Button href="#about" text="More About Us" />
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .purpose-journey-panel {
    background-color: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-grey);
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  }

  .split-left {
    grid-column: 2 / 24;
    margin-bottom: 6rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .split-left {
      grid-column: 2 / 12;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      position: sticky;
      top: 15rem;
      align-self: start;
    }
  }

  .header-text {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-black);
  }

  .quote {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .quote {
      font-size: 5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }
  }

  .split-right {
    grid-column: 2 / 24;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .split-right {
      grid-column: 13 / 23;
    }
  }

  .heading {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .heading {
      font-size: 3.6rem;
    }
  }

  .journey-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .paragraph {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .scripture {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-grey);
    padding-left: 2.5rem;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-grey);
    margin: 3rem 0;
    margin-left: 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .reference {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
  }


</style>
